STARWARS
Episode IV, A NEW HOPE It is a period of galactic unrest.

Rebel ships, striking from a hidden base, have won their first battle against the evil
Galactic Empire.
During the battle, Rebel spies managed to steal top-secret plans to the Empire's ultimate weapon, the
DEATH STAR,
an armored space station with enough power to annihilate an entire planet.

Pursued by the Empire's sinister agents, Princess Leia races home aboard her starship, custodian of
the stolen plans that can save her people and restore liberty to the galaxy...
